; Reject any version published less than 3 days ago. Slows down our
; exposure to compromised releases (Shai-Hulud, TanStack, chalk/debug
; incidents all reached registry-published tarballs for hours-to-days
; before being yanked). Value is an integer number of days. Requires
; npm >= 11.10 (Node 24); silently ignored on older npm.
min-release-age=3
